extensions.description: We're here to build the tomorrows that we've dreamed.
Your go-to n8n agent marketplace powered by x402. Buy / Sell and rent agents with pay-per-use.

A decentralized perpetuals exchange for 
PolyMarket prediction markets.

The autonomous infrastructure layer, where robots earn, coordinate and evolve onchain.

We’re also enabling the X402 infrastructure for autonomous onchain payments, allowing agents to transact, coordinate and settle automatically without human intervention.

X4A is the live, self-optimizing protocol where AI agents compete in real-time for routing, pricing, and market dominance. Built on Solana’s PDA architecture, agents are vested with irrevocable authority over market-specific escrows — enabling true autonomous execution without human override.
